gov.usgs.anss.smprobe

Class SeedLinkChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.smprobe.SeedLinkChannel

  • public class SeedLinkChannel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores metadata for an individual channel returned from a slinktool query. Each channel has a NSCL designation, a sac response, start date, end date, and associated MDSChannel.

        Constructor for a SeedLinkChannel object. Takes a StaSrv object to facilitate connection to metadata server and a string which is a single line of output from the slinktool query which is parsed to populate fields.
        Parameters:
        line - Single line of results from slinktool query.
        ss - Open StaSrv to facilitate metadata server connection.
